         <h2 class="tnm_headings" id="Cookies">5. Cookies</h2>
        <p class="tnm_content">To enrich and perfect your online experience, Vishuddha Crops uses "Cookies", similar technologies and
            services provided by others to display personalised content, appropriate advertising and store your
            preferences on your computer.</p>
        <p class="tnm_content">A cookie is a string of information that a website stores on a visitor's computer, and that the visitor's
            browser provides to the website each time the visitor returns. Vishuddha Crops uses cookies to help
            Vishuddha Crops identify and track visitors, their usage of https://vishuddhacrops.com/, and their website
            access preferences. Vishuddha Crops visitors who do not wish to have cookies placed on their computers
            should set their browsers to refuse cookies before using Vishuddha Crops's websites, with the drawback that
            certain features of Vishuddha Crops's websites may not function properly without the aid of cookies.</p>
        <p class="tnm_content">By continuing to navigate our website without changing your cookie settings, you hereby acknowledge and agree
            to Vishuddha Crops's use of cookies.</p>

